{"tid":1652770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"呢條係咪白虎山蓮塘口岸送中之路？？？","createTime":"2019-10-13T19:46:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T16:22:30.000Z","uid":137160,"like":15,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"38c5257d9ef7b9ca99d8c3157d6bfb5ebc334f27","tid":1652770,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:46:10.000Z","msg":"圖1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8XMxaZB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8XMxaZB.jpg&h=c6746ed8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n首先綜合基巴post,出現左幾個常提到既地方<br />\n1. 白虎山行動基地<br />\n2. 蓮塘口岸 <br />\n3. 大陸<br />\n4. 新屋嶺<br />\n5. 燒烤場6號<br />\n6. 懷疑蓄洪池位置<br />\n言而我暫時只link到白虎山行動基地，蓄洪池，蓮塘口岸和大陸，因為地理位置較近<br />\n圖2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idVmOMg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidVmOMg.jpg&h=6b3b4175&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖3.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uyzF4jB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuyzF4jB.jpg&h=357e494d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其怪點：<br />\n由白虎山開始行去蓮塘既路線顯示紅紅橙橙 (圖2示），即係人流都唔算少，但係睇返衛星圖，行山路線應該係白線對上少少既位置(圖3示），咁點解果個冇路既位會係heat map上顯示到一條路線？ ps. 已經filter左行車gps,所以理應冇地圖移位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1AxVuZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1AxVuZ.jpg&h=deb1935f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n同埋隔離post巴打話白虎山果個位懷疑有蓄洪池，同白虎山開始行去蓮塘既路線有異常人流不謀而合。"},{"pid":"483f3e1414f51c5557c83629ec0349745b4386e5","tid":1652770,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:49:14.000Z","msg":"訓哂?"},{"pid":"8af63c33f8357f9b144026b3e67f4cc7bf670b83","tid":1652770,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:51:21.000Z","msg":"dllm"},{"pid":"c5f03f89d629d30dab88e558002c7ee5836bd7ae","tid":1652770,"uid":88743,"like":7,"dislike":14,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:53:01.000Z","msg":"醒下啦<br />\n開個strava睇兩眼又覺得自己發現左個核彈<br />\n做乜鳩啫<br />\n唔好再開咁撚多條明知無結果既戰線