"uid":300860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c5f03f89d629d30dab88e558002c7ee5836bd7ae","tid":1652770,"uid":88743,"like":7,"dislike":14,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:53:01.000Z","msg":"醒下啦<br />\n開個strava睇兩眼又覺得自己發現左個核彈<br />\n做乜鳩啫<br />\n唔好再開咁撚多條明知無結果既戰線啦<br />\n冷氣軍師想搵存在感?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T20:26:53.000Z","msg":"咩叫無結果既戰線 依加啲死黑警死口唔認 唔通等佢地良心發現 主動認罪?? 咁不如自己查喇 人地查呢啲野你估無風險?"},{"pid":"8fd8399232937dff3676064577092629a0f9b483","tid":1652770,"uid":26770,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T22:30:05.000Z","msg":"剛剛想起風水佬講<br />\n西方白虎高<br />\n殺人不用刀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知大家唔信,但中共係迷信開"},{"pid":"dbb68a8d85f98eb2308e7f020c697cd525f6991d","tid":1652770,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T22:43:45.000Z","msg":"朝早有冇人"},{"pid":"b18de97e1ea94de079c12cf2970ac879ccd03b3f","tid":1652770,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:47:23.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"cf52a7de21f12c39b7dc8c69e66b4b503d09386c","tid":1652770,"uid":209241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T03:50:54.000Z","msg":"今朝先追完post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n擺番個懶人包先 credit: 當我發噏瘋 #39924<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家先睇再講野</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n你可以話唔撚信法神之說<br />\n但你唔可以否應係呢樣野<br />\n係Iamgay 巴提出黎<br />\n我地呢幾日先搵到新戰線<br />\n<br />\n唔知頭唔知路既人睇我以下既整合<br />\n<br />\n（資料太多只重點）<br />\n<br />\n首先有位自稱識少少通靈既Iamgay巴比左啲<br />\n從來冇人提過留意過既地點比網民<br />\n<br />\n包括<br />\n香園圍 白虎山 蓄洪池 蓮塘 新屋嶺<br />\n<br />\n經過一論揭尾故咁推理之後，大家發現831離期失蹤既手足好可能會入左太子既蓄洪池<br />\n亦發現香港地底既蓄洪池四通八達 而且有隧道可以直到以上既幾個地方。<br />\n<br />\n所以先有新屋嶺2.0既post出現。政府亦急急解話！<br />\n<br />\n當中仲有好多疑點：<br />\n太子100個手足去左邊<br />\n地道有冇直通中國？<br />\n平時蓄洪池有冇秘密用途等等<br />\n<br />\n最後，邊撚個再屌神佛即block"},{"pid":"0f0c37b213b32460254202316d30e8e35c4f6b18","tid":1652770,"uid":223407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5f03f89d629d30dab88e558002c7ee5836bd7ae","tid":1652770,"uid":88743,"like":7,"dislike":14,"score":-7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:53:01.000Z","msg":"醒下啦<br />\n開個strava睇兩眼又覺得自己發現左個核彈<br />\n做乜鳩啫<br />\n唔好再開咁撚多條明知無結果既戰線啦<br />\n冷氣軍師想搵存在感?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T04:10:53.000Z","msg":"講到成個討論區係你咁"},{"pid":"5841405f0ff3ee980deaca471ef6e72cde3f5cc7","tid":1652770,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:47:42.000Z","msg":"hi"},{"pid":"23170d14d21fbb0fda4b2365f0ff30bb9a627eb7","tid":1652770,"uid":253554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"見太多人講錯，特此介紹番<br />\n<br />\n治理深圳河第4期工程，旨在提升平原河河口至蓮塘/香園圍口岸一段深圳河的防洪水平至可抵禦50年一遇的暴雨。工程包括改善平原河至白虎山一段長約4.5公里的深圳河，及建造容量達80,000立方米的<span style=\"color: red;\">蓄洪湖泊</span><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dsd.gov.hk/Documents/SustainabilityReports/1516/tc/overview_of_flood_prevention.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dsd.gov.hk%2FDocuments%2FSustainabilityReports%2F1516%2Ftc%2Foverview_of_flood_prevention.html&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=f154c62f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dsd.gov.hk/Documents/SustainabilityReports/1516/tc/overview_of_flood_prevention.html</a>"},{"pid":"36d42ee27f30077f0f10314406f53438308620bd","tid":1652770,"uid":263660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"38c5257d9ef7b9ca99d8c3157d6bfb5ebc334f27","tid":1652770,"uid":137160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-13T19:46:10.000Z","msg":"圖1.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8XMxaZB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8XMxaZB.jpg&h=c6746ed8&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n首先綜合基巴post,出現左幾個常提到既地方<br />\n1. 白虎山行動基地<br />\n2. 蓮塘口岸 <br />\n3. 大陸<br />\n4. 新屋嶺<br />\n5. 燒烤場6號<br />\n6. 懷疑蓄洪池位置<br />\n言而我暫時只link到白虎山行動基地，蓄洪池，蓮塘口岸和大陸，因為地理位置較近<br />\n圖2.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/idVmOMg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FidVmOMg.jpg&h=6b3b4175&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n圖3.<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uyzF4jB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuyzF4jB.jpg&h=357e494d&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n其怪點：<br />\n由白虎山開始行去蓮塘既路線顯示紅紅橙橙 (圖2示），即係人流都唔算少，但係睇返衛星圖，行山路線應該係白線對上少少既位置(圖3示），咁點解果個冇路既位會係heat map上顯示到一條路線？ ps. 已經filter左行車gps,所以理應冇地圖移位<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1AxVuZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1AxVuZ.jpg&h=deb1935f&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n同埋隔離post巴打話白虎山果個位懷疑有蓄洪池，同白虎山開始行去蓮塘既路線有異常人流不謀而合。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:12:47.000Z","msg":"match 丫，1234係連住有路"},{"pid":"c0a8af4977befbdfa53d40ad9972ebb316427bab","tid":1652770,"uid":263660,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23170d14d21fbb0fda4b2365f0ff30bb9a627eb7","tid":1652770,"uid":253554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T06:55:08.000Z","msg":"見太多人講錯，特此介紹番<br />\n<br />\n治理深圳河第4期工程，旨在提升平原河河口至蓮塘/香園圍口岸一段深圳河的防洪水平至可抵禦50年一遇的暴雨。工程包括改善平原河至白虎山一段長約4.5公里的深圳河，及建造容量達80,000立方米的<span style=\"color: red;\">蓄洪湖泊</span><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dsd.gov.hk/Documents/SustainabilityReports/1516/tc/overview_of_flood_prevention.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dsd.gov.hk%2FDocuments%2FSustainabilityReports%2F1516%2Ftc%2Foverview_of_flood_prevention.html&d=0ZNtUZ9Qk1f13jNJdsSeN5B82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=f154c62f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dsd.gov.hk/Documents/SustainabilityReports/1516/tc/overview_of_flood_prevention.html</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T08:13:54.000Z","msg":"其實即是會係個湖都好唔代表佢下面冇嘢<br />\n咁上面係運動場下面都可以係蓄洪池喇<br />\n而且佢而家話起湖唔代表唔會改變㗎喎當初設計啫"},{"pid":"8cc1d70991911c33b09427a7543c2e486ecd2ae5","tid":1652770,"uid":253554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c0a8af4977befbdfa53d40ad9972ebb316427bab","t